{"tid":2334120,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"業界選出2020年11部「年度優秀韓劇」《夫妻的世界》&《機智醫生生活》奪下冠亞軍！","createTime":"2020-12-21T03:09:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T03:59:37.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"28e444223efe3ab17408f5abff35dba92c634734","tid":2334120,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T03:09:45.000Z","msg":"2020年在你心目中，最優秀的韓劇是哪一部作品呢？來看看你的眼光是否和專業人士不相上下吧！<br />\n<br />\n昨天分享了業界選出2020年度9部「最令人遺憾」韓劇作品，今天就來分享一下11部業界選出的「最優秀韓劇」吧！<br />\n<br />\n這是由韓國媒體 news1 訪問了20多位業界的專業人士，像是電視台、娛樂、製作公司等等，調查出了今年度「最優秀的11部韓劇」，是否也有你的遺珠之憾呢？換營留言分享。<br />\n<br />\n第一名：《夫妻的世界》10票<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_73b50f17adc8a0abff9f5e977f20ea63/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-20/132456-889726.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_73b50f17adc8a0abff9f5e977f20ea63%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-20%2F132456-889726.jpg&h=e868e897&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二名：《機智醫生生活》5票<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_fe735c299516e773b983cdf044132128/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-20/132456-889727.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_fe735c299516e773b983cdf044132128%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-20%2F132456-889727.jpg&h=ef12b2f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三名：《金牌救援：Stove League》4票<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_f1d86d2e272ce7267d9e68233881b02b/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-20/132456-889728.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_f1d86d2e272ce7267d9e68233881b02b%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-20%2F132456-889728.jpg&h=a7f05f10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第四名：《雖然是精神病但沒關係》2票<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_ea4dcd3eccee13c53b42d2bdb85be764/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-20/132456-889729.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_ea4dcd3eccee13c53b42d2bdb85be764%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-20%2F132456-889729.jpg&h=4f2fb6e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n剩下七部作品也獲得了專業人士1票上榜的肯定：《梨泰院Class》、《惡之花》、《驅魔麵館／驚奇的傳聞》、《屍戰朝鮮2／Kingdom2》、《結過一次了》、《Hyena：富豪辯護人》、《The Penthouse／頂樓》<br />\n<br />\n（圖：JTBC／黃Viu煲劇平台／tvN／SBS）"},{"pid":"36f22a7d3e5d4d112cfa9cc84a02107470f0dcb3","tid":2334120,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T03:10:32.000Z","msg":"頭4都係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b26cf99ca8c5136fb8ed0d62e5255bf8a533e96","tid":2334120,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"36f22a7d3e5d4d112cfa9cc84a02107470f0dcb3","tid":2334120,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T03:10:32.000Z","msg":"頭4都係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T03:11:34.000Z","msg":"Shut the hell up<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f51586ea1389dacbb5f52a844c8c728d543bfba5","tid":2334120,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T03:14:19.000Z","msg":"惡之花 精神病 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cec95f7ecfe57a68c939d62ba86bfceca1a07a03","tid":2334120,"uid":358445,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T03:17:56.000Z","msg":"完全睇唔明精神病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f81e7398b7ab463fbd6167abf58b00e645c630","tid":2334120,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36f22a7d3e5d4d112cfa9cc84a02107470f0dcb3"